# ES Modules

This project uses `"type": "module"`. CommonJS is not supported.

## Import Rules

```js
// ❌ BAD
const express = require('express')
import auth from './middleware/auth'

// ✅ GOOD
import express from 'express'
import auth from './middleware/auth.js'
```

- Always include `.js` extension on local file imports
- `require()` is never allowed
- Dynamic `import()` is fine when needed
